PARAGUAY. Amambay, Cabecera Estrella, Pedro Juan Caballero
<potBibRef id="5F423EE138067154A1B4BD748AF488A9">, Sept. 1933</potBibRef>
, 
<emphasis id="C02C9FFA8256A9B9FEEDC99445E5CDE8" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">T. Rojas</emphasis>
